Description: Image Based Electronic Signatures
Full Description: Vignature provides an image based electronic signature service.   Instead of faxing or overnighting documents to get signatures, businesses can collect signatures through the internet.  Vignature is different from conventional e-signature service providers, however.  Conventional providers only collect non-specific information about the signer, such as an IP address.  Vignature collects an image of the signer.   By accessing a web browser, anyone can upload and email a document for signature. The recipient of the email can review the document, and "click to sign" from a computer, smart phone, or iPad. An image of the signer is captured in real time through a webcam, as he "clicks to sign."  The image of the signer provides an audit trail.
